    public abstract class TigrContigFileParser
extends Object

    TigrContigFileParser can parse TIGR ".contig" formatted files that are produced by legacy TIGR assembly programs.

      • parse

        public abstract void parse(TigrContigFileVisitor visitor,
                           TigrContigFileVisitor.TigrContigVisitorCallback.TigrContigVisitorMemento memento)
                    throws IOException
        Parse the contig file from starting from the position provided by the given memento and call the appropriate visit methods on the given visitor.
        Specified by:
        parse in interface TigrContigParser
        Parameters:
        visitor - the visitor instance to call the visit methods on as the file is parsed.
        memento - the TigrContigFileVisitor.TigrContigVisitorCallback.TigrContigVisitorMemento instance to tell the parser where to start parsing from; can not be null.
        Throws:
        IOException - if there are any problems parsing the contig file.
        NullPointerException - if either visitor or memento are null.
        UnsupportedOperationException - if the parser implementation does not support mementos.
        IllegalArgumentException - if the memento instance was produced by this class.
        See Also:
        TigrContigParser.canParse()
